Package: Palindrome
Title: Turns a number into a Palindrome by reversing and adding
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Tony", "Ladson", , "tony.ladson@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: Tests if a number is a palindrome. If not, reverse the number and add. Repeat until the number is a palindrome.
